<div class="d-panels font-secondary-light">
<div id="aip_a" class="d-panel p" style="display: none">
<div class="p" id="af0005">
<sup>a</sup>Division of Pulmonary, Allergy, and Critical Care Medicine, Department of Medicine, Columbia University Vagelos College of Physicians &amp; Surgeons/NewYork-Presbyterian Hospital, New York, NY, USA</div>
<div id="af0010">
